Offering almost 50 squares of luxury living this home provides every type of informal and formal living/entertaining space you can think of and is located only a short stroll from all of Derrimuts amenities. Other features include ducted heating, evaporative cooling, high ceilings, security shutters, down lights, rendered facade, stainless steel appliances, alarm , landscaped gardens and double garage with remote.

Perfect first home or Investment

Comprising three generous sized bedrooms, master with WIR & en-suite and two remaining bedrooms also offering built in robes. Bright central bathroom with easy access from the living room and remaining bedrooms, large tiled meals area and a spacious lounge, perfect for any host to entertain. Heading outdoors, you're presented with a fully concreted outside entertaining area and good sized rear yard. Don't delay and enquire today!

Description:
When only the best will do.
Family living in Derrimut has a new benchmark. Combining cutting-edge design and high quality fittings, this 5 bedroom, 2 bathroom home will take your breath away. Set on a generous size block, this absolute gem is awaiting the homeowner who wants it all. Showcasing impeccable workmanship alongside modern family Luxury living in one of Derrimut's finest locations. The interior is instantly eye-catching with its wide entrance flowing throughout the ground level.
The gourmet kitchen highlights the home's luxury and detail with a caesarstone bench and ample cupboard storage. The very best stainless steel appliances including a 900mm gas cooker, glass splashback and a walk-in pantry.
Comprising of five great-sized bedrooms, retreat to master with large ensuite, separate study with its own balcony, dining area and adjoining spacious family room. Enjoy your favourite movies in your own theatre room, or entertain family and friends outside with the decked alfresco area together with the Bali inspired gazebo. Upstairs there is a great-sized secondary lounge room which is ideal for a children's retreat. Other features include, ducted heating, evaporative cooling, video intercom, internal access from the double garage, external gas line for your BBQ, 5 star rating batts in all walls and ceilings, plantation shutters, beautiful landscaped front and rear gardens.
The home is ideally located in the heart of Derrimut and within close proximity to Balmoral Park, schools, transport, freeway and a choice of shopping precincts. Nothing could be finer.
Disclaimer: Every precaution has been taken to establish the accuracy of the above information but it does not constitute any representation by the vendor or agent.
Cameron Vurovecz : 0431 945 737

Description:
Impressive Inside - Amazing Outside
Amazing outside spaces complimented by a much loved and cared for interior combine to offer the perfect family friendly residence. A superb open plan kitchen overlooks the large dining and main living area and provides access and views of the magnificent backyard highlighted by an enormous pergola which is perfect for outside entertaining or doubles as a great undercover storage area for a boat or caravan by utilising the rear roller door access of the double remote garage. A separate lounge/theatre room, luxurious master suite featuring dual WIRs, double vanity and double shower ensuite , and 3 additional bedrooms with mirrored BIRs serviced by a lovely central bathroom with spa complete the home. Other features include ducted heating, 2 reverse cycle air conditioners, brand new carpets, alarm, 900mm appliances and dishwasher in kitchen, 2 outdoor sheds, 14,000 litre water tank, huge backyard (approx. 640sqm allotment) with a cubby house that the kids will love, vegetable patch for the keen gardener, artificial grass and mature hedges that provide privacy from neighbours . All this in a prized location walking distance to all amenities.
